readonly cache="${alfred_workflow_cache}/cache.json"
# If cache does not exist, build it now if [[ ! -f "${cache}" ]]; then osascript -e "tell application id \"com.runningwithcrayons.Alfred\" to run trigger \"rebuild_cache\" in workflow \"${alfred_workflow_bundleid}\""
until [[ -f "${cache}" ]]; do sleep 0.2 done fi
cat "${cache}"
